{"type":"message","id":"4e25b228","parentId":"de8d85d2","timestamp":"2026-02-08T06:57:57.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到了问题！从错误日志可以看出，Telegram插件仍然无法连接到Telegram服务器（`setMyCommands failed: Network request for 'setMyCommands' failed!`），即使我们设置了环境变量，但似乎还不够。我需要找到一个更好的方法来为Telegram插件配置代理。\n\n让我检查OpenClaw的文档或配置选项，看看是否有专门针对频道插件的代理设置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fde4e7e500054b319495f0c6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw doctor"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":4081,"output":108,"cacheRead":23744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27933,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770533874513}}
