{"type":"message","id":"341b268c","parentId":"5ae21802","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:52:22.376Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user wants me to write a blog post about 罗翔 (Luo Xiang) following the prompt rules. Let me first do web search to gather information about him, then write the article.\n\nKey points from the prompt:\n- Network爆款 article style\n- Remove AI痕迹, humanized language\n- Storytelling with suspense, golden quotes\n- Insert relevant online images\n- At least 10 authoritative sources (I'll simulate this by doing thorough research)\n- Positive and uplifting\n- Detailed emotional descriptions, real scenes, dialogues\n- Suitable for 小红书/微信公众号\n\n罗翔 is a famous Chinese law professor who became popular through Bilibili for his engaging and humorous legal education videos. He's known for his \"thick description\" of criminal cases, using absurd hypothetical scenarios to explain legal principles. <|tool_calls_section_begin|> <|tool_call_begin|>  functions.web_search:25 <|tool_call_argument_begin|> {\"query\": \"罗翔 教授 个人经历 成长故事 教育背景\", \"count\": 10, \"search_lang\": \"zh\"} <|tool_call_end|> <|tool_call_begin|>  functions.web_search:26 <|tool_call_argument_begin|> {\"query\": \"罗翔 B站 爆红 厚大 刑法 教学风格\", \"count\": 10, \"search_lang\": \"zh\"} <|tool_call_end|> <|tool_call_begin|>  functions.web_search:27 <|tool_call_argument_begin|> {\"query\": \"罗翔 经典语录 金句 人生感悟 正义\", \"count\": 10, \"search_lang\": \"zh\"} <|tool_call_end|> <|tool_calls_section_end|>","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":21238,"output":283,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21521,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770540737883}}
