{"type":"message","id":"3a9abf03","parentId":"74f366c5","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:54:01.561Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 用户让我写罗翔的人物博客。我需要先进行网络调研，了解罗翔的最新信息，然后按照prompt的要求写一篇去AI化、有真实感、有人情味的人物博客。\n\n让我先搜索罗翔的相关信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"  连接正常！正在调研罗翔的最新信息，马上写出来 📝   "},{"type":"toolCall","id":" functions.web_search:27","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"罗翔 厚大 法考 段子手 法外狂徒张三","count":10,"search_lang":"zh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":" functions.web_search:25","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"罗翔 2024 2025 最新动态 普法 现状","count":10,"search_lang":"zh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":" functions.web_search:26","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"罗翔 刑法 讲课 传奇经历 人生故事","count":10,"search_lang":"zh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":21221,"output":188,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21409,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770540839051}}
