{"type":"message","id":"578317f0","parentId":"b4468ce1","timestamp":"2026-02-08T09:05:28.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The cron scheduler is enabled and working, but there are currently no jobs. I should explain what can be done with cron jobs and ask what kind of scheduled task they want to create.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"      <final>\n可以的！✅ **Cron 定时任务功能已启用**\n\n**当前状态：**\n- ✅ 调度器运行中\n- 📁 任务存储：`~/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json`\n- 📊 现有任务：0 个\n\n---\n\n**支持的定时任务类型：**\n\n| 类型 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **every** | 定期执行 | 每30分钟检查一次邮件 |\n| **at** | 一次性定时 | 今晚8点提醒我开会 |\n| **cron** | Cron表达式 | 每周一早9点生成周报 |\n\n**任务可以做的事：**\n- 🔔 发送提醒/通知（到任意频道）\n- 🤖 运行子代理执行复杂任务\n- 📝 检查邮箱/日历/天气\n- 📊 生成报告或汇总\n- 🔧 自动执行脚本或命令\n\n---\n\n**你想创建什么样的定时任务？** 🤔\n\n例如：\n- \"每天早上8点推送天气\"\n- \"每小时检查一次邮件，有重要邮件就通知我\"\n- \"每周五下午5点写周报\"\n- \"今晚10点提醒我早睡\"\n\n告诉我具体需求，我立刻帮你设置！🚀\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":30947,"output":301,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31248,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770541525222}}
