{"type":"message","id":"0d681aa0","parentId":"133f00a3","timestamp":"2026-02-08T12:18:03.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 用户让我继续写人物博客文章并提交到 GitHub。我需要：\n1. 先查看 notebook 项目里已有的人物博客，避免重复\n2. 选择一个要写的新人物\n3. 写文章\n4. 提交到 GitHub\n\n让我先列出已有的文章，看看写了谁，然后选一个合适的来写。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"  functions.exec:64","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -1 ~/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/*.md | sort"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":34643,"output":100,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34743,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770553079988}}
{"type":"message","id":"56017790","parentId":"0d681aa0","timestamp":"2026-02-08T12:18:03.370Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"  functions.exec:64","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/1.musk-2025-tech-progress.20250928.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/10.yang-mi-actress-boss.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/11.su-bingtian-flying-man.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/12.yao-ming-basketball-giant.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/13.mo-yan-nobel-laureate.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/14.li-ziqi-cultural-exporter.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/15.hui-ruoqi-volleyball-captain.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/16.ma-yun-ecommerce-emperor.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/17.luo-xiang-legal-philosopher.20250208.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/2.trump-business-legend.20250928.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/2025-09-29-leijun-the-man-who-survived.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/3.steve-jobs-legend.20250928.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/4.bill-gates-philanthropy-legend.20250930.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/5.leijun-2025-tech-legend.20251006.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/6.gu-ailing-champion-story.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/7.yuzuru-hanyu-ice-prince.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/8.zhang-yimou-director-legend.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/9.ma-jiaqi-teen-idol.20251013.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":22,"aggregated":"/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/1.musk-2025-tech-progress.20250928.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/10.yang-mi-actress-boss.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/11.su-bingtian-flying-man.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/12.yao-ming-basketball-giant.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/13.mo-yan-nobel-laureate.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/14.li-ziqi-cultural-exporter.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/15.hui-ruoqi-volleyball-captain.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/16.ma-yun-ecommerce-emperor.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/17.luo-xiang-legal-philosopher.20250208.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/2.trump-business-legend.20250928.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/2025-09-29-leijun-the-man-who-survived.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/3.steve-jobs-legend.20250928.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/4.bill-gates-philanthropy-legend.20250930.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/5.leijun-2025-tech-legend.20251006.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/6.gu-ailing-champion-story.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/7.yuzuru-hanyu-ice-prince.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/8.zhang-yimou-director-legend.20251013.md\n/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/notebook/person-doc/9.ma-jiaqi-teen-idol.20251013.md","cwd":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1770553083366}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2c1fa83","parentId":"56017790","timestamp":"2026-02-08T12:18:09.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  已有的人物包括：\n国际：马斯克、特朗普、乔布斯、比尔·盖茨\n中国：雷军（2篇）、杨幂、苏炳添、姚明、莫言、李子柒、惠若琪、马云、罗翔\n体育：谷爱凌、羽生结弦\n导演：张艺谋\n娱乐：马嘉祺\n\n我可以写一个科技界的热门人物，比如：\n1. 黄仁勋（英伟达 CEO，AI 时代的代表人物）\n2. Sam Altman（OpenAI CEO）- 可能比较敏感\n3. 张一鸣（字节跳动创始人）\n4. 任正非（华为）\n5. 刘强东（京东）\n\n黄仁勋最近很火，AI 算力之王，值得写。让我写一篇黄仁勋的文章，然后提交。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" 了解了！目前 **17篇** 人物博客，涵盖：\n\n**国际：** 马斯克、特朗普、乔布斯、比尔·盖茨  \n**中国企业家：** 雷军(2篇)、马云  \n**运动员：** 苏炳添、姚明、谷爱凌、羽生结弦、惠若琪  \n**文化/艺术：** 莫言、李子柒、张艺谋、罗翔  \n**娱乐：** 杨幂、马嘉祺\n\n---\n\n**建议写谁？** 🤔\n\n**科技大佬选项：**\n- 🟢 **黄仁勋** — 英伟达CEO，\"AI算力之王\"，2025年身价暴涨\n- 🟢 **张一鸣** — 字节跳动创始人，TikTok之父\n- 🟢 **任正非** — 华为创始人，科技突围代表\n\n**你点名，我立刻开写！** 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":35255,"output":340,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35595,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770553083370}}
