{"type":"message","id":"37927a32","parentId":"abab31d8","timestamp":"2026-02-08T14:03:30.849Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"  functions.exec:67","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[main dbe1a60] 新增两篇人物博客：黄仁勋（AI教父）和张一鸣（字节跳动创始人）\n 5 files changed, 472 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 person-doc/18.jensen-huang-nvidia-ai-king.20250208.md\n create mode 100644 person-doc/19.zhang-yiming-bytedance-founder.20250208.md\n create mode 100644 tech/img.png\n create mode 100644 tech/img_1.png\n create mode 100644 tech/openclaw.md\nTo https://github.com/Linux2010/notebook.git\n   4e7e790..dbe1a60  main -> main"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2345,"aggregated":"[main dbe1a60] 新增两篇人物博客：黄仁勋（AI教父）和张一鸣（字节跳动创始人）\n 5 files changed, 472 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 person-doc/18.jensen-huang-nvidia-ai-king.20250208.md\n create mode 100644 person-doc/19.zhang-yiming-bytedance-founder.20250208.md\n create mode 100644 tech/img.png\n create mode 100644 tech/img_1.png\n create mode 100644 tech/openclaw.md\nTo https://github.com/Linux2010/notebook.git\n   4e7e790..dbe1a60  main -> main","cwd":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1770559410846}}
{"type":"message","id":"52af834c","parentId":"37927a32","timestamp":"2026-02-08T14:03:47.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  完成了！","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"    完成了！✅\n\n**刚写完并提交到 GitHub：**\n\n1. 🟢 **黄仁勋** —《那个穿皮衣的\"AI教父\"》\n   - 10岁被霸凌的瘦弱男孩 → 61岁万亿帝国掌舵人\n   - 从Denny's洗碗工到斯坦福学霸\n   - 破产边缘的疯狂重生\n\n2. 🟢 **张一鸣** —《那个默默退居幕后的\"算法天才\"》\n   - 38岁卸任CEO的背后故事\n   - 四次失败中找到今日头条\n   - TikTok征服世界的中国产品\n\n**GitHub提交：** ✅ 已推送\n- 文件数：19篇人物博客\n- 提交信息：`新增两篇人物博客...`\n\n还想要什么任务？🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":40480,"output":173,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40653,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770559410849}}
